{"tid":898132,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【士多啤梨插針】澳警拘捕一名涉案女子 未透露動機","createTime":"2018-11-11T12:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T03:44:36.000Z","uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d87e70fc50a28dc67f3ccef9e58bbf6d9246feda","tid":898132,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:49:41.000Z","msg":"澳洲多地自9月出現「士多啤梨插針」案，警方周日表示，經過複雜詳細的調查後已拘捕一名女子。<br />\n警方表示在周日下午拘捕一名50歲女子，她將於同日晚上被起訴，周一於布里斯本法院提堂，但警方尚未透露她的控罪以及犯案動機。<br />\n澳洲多地的超級市場自9月起，發現有人蓄意把縫紉針或大頭針插入士多啤梨、蘋果、香蕉等水果之中，至少一名男子吃到尖針後入院。昆士蘭省當局為此懸紅緝兇，政府也提高相關罪行的刑期以阻嚇。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲新聞網"},{"pid":"2770b2167d146b1c0732ec41aabc6db74a5f2964","tid":898132,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:50:37.000Z","msg":"樓主又"},{"pid":"da0c60be73c01ecab3ef64fdd01b6d3882701b71","tid":898132,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2770b2167d146b1c0732ec41aabc6db74a5f2964","tid":898132,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:50:37.000Z","msg":"樓主又"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"還N賓清白"},{"pid":"93b7ac3f784547493fd86ac7354510a6a2624358","tid":898132,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da0c60be73c01ecab3ef64fdd01b6d3882701b71","tid":898132,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2770b2167d146b1c0732ec41aabc6db74a5f2964","tid":898132,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T12:50:37.000Z","msg":"樓主又"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"還N賓清白"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T13:10:47.000Z","msg":"佢絲黎"},{"pid":"b7f78851c80dd40f7a3ad0d16c043a46ff5b5a5b","tid":898132,"uid":34572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"93b7ac3f784547493fd86ac7354510a6a2624358","tid":898132,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da0c60be73c01ecab3ef64fdd01b6d3882701b71","tid":898132,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":